Sure, here are some examples:

1. *Rusi* su osnovali grad Moskvu. (The *Rus* founded the city of Moscow.)
2. Oni *ruše* zgradu da bi sagradili novu. (They are *tearing down* the building to build a new one.)
3. *Rušenje* starog mosta trajalo je tri dana. (The *demolition* of the old bridge lasted three days.)
4. Njihova vojska *rušila* je gradove duž puta. (Their army *destroyed* cities along the way.)
5. Čujem da *rušiš* staru kuću. (I hear you're *knocking down* an old house.)
6. *Ruševine* starog zamka još uvijek stoje na brdu. (The *ruins* of the old castle still stand on the hill.)
7. Oni su *razrušili* cijelu ulicu kako bi napravili novi trg. (They *razed* the whole street to build a new square.)
8. *Ruski* jezik koriste ljudi u Rusiji. (People in Russia use the *Russian* language.)
9. Kip slobode u New Yorku dizajnirao je *ruski* kipar. (The Statue of Liberty in New York was designed by a *Russian* sculptor.)
10. Danas je *Rusija* jedna od najvećih zemalja na svijetu. (Today, *Russia* is one of the largest countries in the world.)

I hope these examples help! Let me know if you have any questions or if you need further assistance.